            <title>[HBASE-3533] Allow HBASE_LIBRARY_PATH env var to specify extra locations of native libs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3533</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Would be handy when you have native libs at other spots on the system (eg I often want to test hadoop-lzo changes directly out of its build dir)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
